### Test StockChatRoomWeb API Endpoints

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Test123!"
}

### Login with the user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### Send a regular message (replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN with token from login)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/chat/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "content": "Hello everyone!"
}

### Send a stock command (this should NOT be saved to database)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/chat/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "content": "/stock=AAPL.US"
}

### Get recent messages
GET http://localhost:5000/api/chat/messages
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN